# #15-#20 in the build plan are still pending, so don't pre-configure):
#   - Web push notifications (would need VAPID keys)
#   - Resend (email notifications)
#   - Twilio (SMS notifications)
#   - Uber Direct (delivery integration)
#   - Any AI/LLM provider key (menu importer)
# =============================================================================
